OL,6,FI have a few more reflections to share
OL,7,Fon Chancellor Rachel Reeves' Spring
OL,8,FStatement that we'll hear on Wednesday.
OL,10,FThe first is that the Office for
OL,11,FBudget Responsibility is bound to make
OL,12,Fa gloomier forecast for real household
OL,13,Fdisposable income - a proxy for our
OL,14,Fliving standards - than even the
OL,15,Fpretty gloomy forecast it made in
OL,16,FOctober.
OL,18,FBack then, it said Real Household
OL,19,FDisposable Income (RHDI) would rise in
OL,20,Fthis parliament a paltry 0.5% a year
OL,21,Fon average.
