OL,6,FSneeze and any rise in our living
OL,7,Fstandards would vanish.
OL,9,FThere's been a sneezing fit.
OL,11,FWell, as I reported last week, it is
OL,12,Fdowngrading this year's GDP growth
OL,13,Fforecast from 2% to 1%, and will also
OL,14,Fcut its forecast for next year from
OL,15,F1.8%.
OL,17,FThereafter I assume it will stick with
OL,18,Fits forecast for growth of around 1.5%
OL,19,Fper annum for the rest of the
OL,20,Fparliament.
