OL,6,FBut perhaps most significant of all,
OL,7,Fthe government's choice to reduce
OL,8,Fpayments to the disabled and
OL,9,Fincapacitated by #6 billion a year
OL,10,Fwill significantly reduce the living
OL,11,Fstandards of the losers and bring down
OL,12,Fthe average rise in RHDI.
OL,14,FI wouldn't be at all surprised if the
OL,15,Fforecast increases in living standards
OL,16,Fhave been wiped out completely.
