OL,6,FWhich is bad news for all of us, and
OL,7,Fterrible political news for Prime
OL,8,FMinister Keir Starmer - because it was
OL,9,Fonly a few weeks ago that he said his
OL,10,Ftop priority for the parliament was to
OL,11,Fincrease RHDI in every region of the
OL,12,FUK.
OL,14,FSo when the OBR announces the
OL,15,Fdisappointing prediction, you can bet
OL,16,Fthe falling value of your house that
OL,17,FStarmer will say he is minded to go
OL,18,F"further and faster" to reform the
OL,19,Feconomy and revive living standards -
OL,20,Fand will cross fingers and toes.
