OL,6,FI have two other facts to share.
OL,8,FThe first is that Reeves will only
OL,9,Fmake spending and welfare cuts that
OL,10,Frestore her eroded fiscal headroom of
OL,11,Fa short #9.9 billion, rather than
OL,12,Fincrease it.
OL,14,FThis is a pretty racy bet by her.
OL,15,FShe's taking a big economic and
OL,16,Fpolitical risk in not increasing
OL,17,Fheadroom to double or treble that.
OL,19,FThe point is that #9.9 billion is
OL,20,Falmost no buffer or headroom at all.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
