OL,6,FFinally here is a treat for the fiscal
OL,7,Fgeeks.
OL,9,FReeves has had a lucky fiscal windfall
OL,10,Ffrom the decision to fund the pledged
OL,11,F#6 billion a year rise in defence
OL,12,Fspending with a #6 billion cut in
OL,13,Foverseas aid.
OL,15,FWell, the development budget is
OL,16,Fresource (RDEL) whereas most of
OL,17,Fdefence is capital (CDEL).
OL,19,FNow please don't deafen me with your
OL,20,Fcries of "you what?!!!!!" I'll explain.
